Small exercise to learn scrapy framework
The goal is to get all bags from http://www.forzieri.com


WHAT DOES IT DO:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 - scraping all the page containing bags items, and get relative informations
 - download bags images
 - put all the bags items into the forzieri.com_products.xml file


DEPENDENCIES :
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 - scrapy


HOW TO USE :
~~~~~~~~~~~~
 # python scrapy-ctl.py crawl forzieri.com
